=== 招聘信息 ===
 
 公司名称:北京铿腾电子科技有限公司 
 招聘职位:AMS RnD Software Engineer[急聘]  
 截至日期:2005-11-22  
 最低学历:硕士  
 招聘人数:人 
 工作地点: 北京 
 简历投递处: http://www.jobmm.com/cadence/Kuntai_job.asp 
 
岗位描述:  
Job Description:
-Candidate will be involved in Development, enhancement and maintain mixed 
 signal circuit simulator which support Verilog-A, VHDL-AMS in spice netlist.
-Candidate will be in charged of integrating our AMS product into Matlab
 enviroment.
-Candidate will be involved in GUI integrating AMS product into Cadence 
 GUI flow.
 
相关要求: 
Required
-BS in CS/EE or similar level of expertise with at least 2 years of 
 working experience.
-Must with coding experience in C, C++, Perl/TCL
 Better has experience of using SKILL(Cadence programming language)
-Must have Matlab/Simulink experience
-At least some knowledge of Analog/Mixed Signal.
-Be capable of understanding system design.
 Better if have System design/architecture experience 
   
